= Research Projects

== Information-theoretic Security and Cryptography
~~~
{*Bit Commitment Protocols*}\n
*Collaborators:* [http://www.facweb.iitkgp.ac.in/~amitalok/ Amitalok J. Budkuley] (supervisor), [https://www.niser.ac.in/users/manojmishra Manoj Mishra] (co-supervisor), [ Manideep Mamindlapally], and Pranav Joshi\n

Bit Commitment is a fundamental and widely studied cryptograhpic primitive with multitudinous applications in secure Multiparty Computation (MPC), Blockchains, Contract signing, Zero-knowledge proofs, etc.


